# How to make foundry project without `foundry init` by mylord jtriley
# 1. Make directories
mkdir src out lib script

# 2. Specify those directories in `foundry.toml` (see https://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/blob/master/config/README.md)

# 3. Add `forge-std` module to `lib`

git submodule add https://github.com/foundry-rs/forge-std lib/forge-std


# 3.5.  Run `git submodule update --init --recursive` in case the submodule gives problems
# 4. Start creating contracts!